&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CDF: The CDF of normal distribution doesn&#39;t have a closed form, i.e., there is no analytic answer of the integral  正态分布的 CDF 没有封闭形式，即没有积分的解析答案&lt;/p&gt;
