&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/d51m9S2LJ7cylnx.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;CT前面切面&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/byLt9WVezE1BCj3.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;膈面，后下面&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/qurwj8cBt9AYE5T.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;三缘&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/DJOzCYHWP4612Fv.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;右侧锐缘支，左侧钝缘支&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/t4HolYAJXvPeTLj.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;三沟&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;胸片影像&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#胸片影像&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 胸片影像&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;正位&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#正位&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 正位&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;gallery&#34;&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/RzCdtLebi17jIXk.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;上腔静脉 Superior Vena Cava, SVC&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/iSTsVDfqb2FjaUM.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;奇静脉 Azygos Vein&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/4RauPxsVhTXe6tD.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;右肺动、静脉 Right Pulmonary Artery/Vein&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/gmLaYlR763cpPH1.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;右心房 Right Atrium&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/5dRo6t9EybxYiqs.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;左锁骨下动脉 Left Subclavian Artery&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/7WviJLEuP8fNxYg.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;主动脉弓和降主动脉 Aorta Arch and Descending Aorta&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/vRwQuxPYfq2bXWD.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;左肺动、静脉 Left Pulmonary Artery/Vein&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/DdxjwRzOlhcFNSt.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;左心耳 Left Atrial Appendage&#34; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/gwPrd3fT6jOQpEy.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;左心室 Left Ventricle&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;右前斜-rao&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#右前斜-rao&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 右前斜 RAO&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;观察右心房、肺动脉主干、右心室&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;胸骨在心脏前面&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;脊柱和食管在心脏后面&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/NzvOusEHCP5gixT.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;RAO 30度&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;左前斜-lao&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#左前斜-lao&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 左前斜 LAO&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;观察左心室、右心房、右心室、主动脉弓&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://i.loli.net/2021/07/25/eIgjzktU6cSC7rH.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;LAO 45度&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
